    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "Imam al-Sadiq (AS) describes a special prayer of four units in which Surah al-Ikhlas is recited fifty times per unit, totaling two hundred recitations. This prayer guarantees complete forgiveness of all sins. The teaching was narrated through Abu Basir, one of the Imam's closest companions, in the context of devotional practices that bring believers closer to divine mercy.",
